### 5.1 Query Comparison

**Current Implementation** (basic task show):
```
Query 1: SELECT * FROM tasks WHERE id = ?
Total: 1 query, ~50 bytes
```

**New Implementation** (full context):
```
Core Queries (always):
  Query 1: Task + Work Item JOIN       ‚Üí ~500 bytes
  Query 2: Project                     ‚Üí ~300 bytes
  Query 3: All 6W contexts            ‚Üí ~2KB

Supporting Queries (conditional):
  Query 4: Documents (if exist)        ‚Üí ~1KB
  Query 5: Evidence (if exist)         ‚Üí ~1KB
  Query 6: Recent events               ‚Üí ~500 bytes
  Query 7: Latest summary (if exist)   ‚Üí ~500 bytes
  Query 8: Dependencies (if exist)     ‚Üí ~300 bytes

Total: 3-8 queries, ~2.5KB-6KB data
```

